<%# Features Section %>
<div id="features">
	<div class="container">
		<h1 align="center">Features of ziada</h1><br>
		<div class="row">
			<h5 align="center">Ziada is a cloud based software for managing retail businesses. It includes Sale, Inventory, Accounting and Employee Management all Happening Online. The entrepreneur's haven</h5>
			<h5 align="center">So then, what do I benefit from all this?</h5>
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-cubes"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">Make more money</h5>
				<p>Say goodbye to poor management. Ziada offers robust consistency of information collected from sales, purchases,
				customer and users. You wont lose money because of errors made by either you or your employees when handling heaps and heaps of receipts. If you're not losing money, chances are that you're making it.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-lock"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">No more employee theft</h5>
				<p>Your business may be making more money but you're not. Guess what, someone else is. That someone just may be your employee. Ziada being an online service, allows you to be virtually present in your business. With real time transaction updates, you can know, what and how many products sold, how much cash in hand is available and employees involved in transactions.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-users"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">More people working with you</h5>
				<p>Great things can be achieved when people work together. Ziada allows you to have multiple user accounts in your business account enabling you to arrive at your goals faster. You can assign roles of users based on what you want them to do </p>
			</div>
		</div> <br><!-- .row-->

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-line-chart"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">Informed decision making</h5>
				<p>Decisions are what decide the future of your business. They can be scary and you can't run away from them. So if you are going to make one, better make an informed one. Ziada provides basic reports. Advanced reports are also generated by the ziada management team when you request for them.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
				<i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>
				<h5 class="feature-header">You get more time</h5>
				<p>We saved the best for last. One of the benefits of entrepreneurship is freedom. Ziada enhances that benefit. You can manage your business anywhere and anytime from any device as long as you can access the internet.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<br>
